{"tid":1984863,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"［求解夢] 一人N個好怪異既夢","createTime":"2020-04-22T18:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T08:29:23.000Z","uid":355244,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"b654740f14cd0d6f08d26ace2ee72cefbde6551e","tid":1984863,"uid":355244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:00:32.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小學到初中連續5-6年 間中發到同一個夢<br />\n個夢係我係一個好黑好舊既商場 準備搭好窄既自動電梯落下層<br />\n點知一踏腳就一路碌落地下 之後離心力勁得滯就會嚇醒左<br />\n但次次一醒都係清晨五點幾 隻腳都係抬起左 好似真係碌左落去果個姿勢咁<br />\n但上左高中就冇再發過 唔知個夢有咩寓意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋試過發夢 用第三身角度<br />\n高處望到自己係張床度訓教<br />\n但係成個人不斷被無形既力升起 又將我個人180度咁轉黎轉去 又推落地 個感覺好撚真實 諗返都覺得驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bf468fa72fe5b2c5cc33505ee7e69e0aae5083","tid":1984863,"uid":261812,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你張床有冇對住鏡？"},{"pid":"1439adcb7eb55b57c2b0a5298bff655d905b4384","tid":1984863,"uid":248536,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:04:08.000Z","msg":"發夢見到自己係住嘅公共屋村搭𨋢嗰陣無啦啦去到80幾樓，明明得40層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後出左𨋢重要一直去唔翻自已住嗰層 cls"},{"pid":"f734d2b2a7aa545d2dbc43cb79671688de4a48de","tid":1984863,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:05:22.000Z","msg":"咩叫電梯 唔通有手動電梯？"},{"pid":"a1587b721698d55a77d0c37cbea4283804107b94","tid":1984863,"uid":322685,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1439adcb7eb55b57c2b0a5298bff655d905b4384","tid":1984863,"uid":248536,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:04:08.000Z","msg":"發夢見到自己係住嘅公共屋村搭𨋢嗰陣無啦啦去到80幾樓，明明得40層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後出左𨋢重要一直去唔翻自已住嗰層 cls"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:08:47